    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<strong>The land of Acadia is tainted, weathered, <i>raw</i>, and you have been unlucky enough to find yourself on this forsaken isle...</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157290/extras/f5ef78fb58fa6250e10a31e1126dde01.avif?t=1721418749\" width=700 height=80 /></span><br><br>Azarine Heart is an open-world RPG, where choices, actions, and words all matter. Like the butterfly effect, a small action can have unforeseen consequences. Stranded on the isle of Acadia, a small but important island off the mainland of Ralvan, you must find your way through Blight-ridden camps, dust storms, vicious bandits and killers, dangerous wildlife, and above all else, your own pitiful self, with only one goal; to find <i>her</i>. Nothing matters but her, your sister, robbed from you by cultists in the night. Forced into choices that will decide the fate of Acadia and its people, what will you do, what will you <i>sacrifice</i>, in her name?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157290/extras/f5ef78fb58fa6250e10a31e1126dde01.avif?t=1721418749\" width=700 height=80 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> An active battle system, where your weapons and skills matter less than your skill and focus.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157290/extras/18dbb8278adc66f92587431cd622b985.avif?t=1721418749\" width=544 height=320 /></span><br></li><li> Over 600 hand-crafted locations, from soaring mountains, to deep woods, to dark caverns below the earth...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157290/extras/95f2ab012a9e6827ee39cb569c7b08f3.avif?t=1721418749\" width=544 height=320 /></span><br></li><li> Willing followers, bound by love or duty, whose goals may differ from yours...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157290/extras/ddc902b498d694038bb2aa4c424d07cf.avif?t=1721418749\" width=544 height=320 /></span><br></li><li> Seven factions, each serving their own purpose in Acadia.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157290/extras/c88bca9a1789979a7a77d4cf9417c688.avif?t=1721418749\" width=544 height=320 /></span><br></li><li> Choices. The fates of people, each with their own lives, or bigger than that. Cities, provinces, the world at large...all lands into <i>your</i> hands. Will you do the right thing? Or will you do something worse...for power?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157290/extras/f5ef78fb58fa6250e10a31e1126dde01.avif?t=1721418749\" width=700 height=80 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Steam Features</h2></li><li> Achievements! Find motivation in serving under all factions, or joining all covenants, or picking apart every corner of Acadia for secrets and hidden gems...literally <i>and</i> metaphorically.<br></li><li> Controller support using Joy-to-Key. Configure this however you'd like using this software, found right in the game files under &quot;Controls&quot;.<br></li><li> Family sharing is also supported!</li></ul>",
